metadata.description:
Angst - Eye (Genesis Music Video NFT)

Produced by Shinjin
Directed by Dexx Visuals

--

Angst is a Filipino-Canadian artist, songwriter and producer based in Vancouver, BC, Canada. 


"My lyrics tend to take my listeners on a tour of my mind; sometimes my lyrics contradict themselves, being bipolar does that.. This track, "Eye" and all of my songs are kind of like a painting that doesn’t just tell a story but expresses what it’s like to be an artist like me."

NFT holder access + benefits: 

-Access to a private Discord channel & unreleased music in the Angst server
-1 custom video shoutout from Angst per NFT (must submit your request via the Angst Discord server by April 30, 2022 - non-transferable)
